name: away3d-core-fp11
description: Away3D is an open source, real time 3D engine for the Flash Platform. The project was started by Alexander Zadorozhny and Rob Bateman in 2007 and has been evolving non-stop ever since. Below is a list of some of the most important features of the Away3D engine. This is a package meant for the experimental purpose of using nodejs to build awesome flash content.
